  <description><![CDATA[ 
    stendhal is a <b>multiplayer</b> online adventures game like Zelda.<br/>
    Your task is to talk with other people in the village and find jobs to do that will drive to 
    interesting quests that will reveal the hidden plot behind the <i>world of stendhal</i><p>
    In Stendhal, you can just walk around, chat with people, buy and sell items and kill some of them :)
    Some of these people are NPC, they will give you tasks to accomplish and hints to solve your quest.<p>
    Stendhal wants to be a reference to investigate Marauroa 1.00 features.]]>
  </description>
